        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2240626363" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14394543062163964798">This story collection is a classic that I plan to read at least one more time. The translation keeps the text flowing with a style that&apos;s simultaneously ancient and contemporary. Also, every tale contains realistic and fantastic elements, and leaves the reader with a handful of ideas to consider afterward. I&apos;d recommend this book to anyone without hesitation.</span>
  <span id="freeText14394543062163964798" style="display:none">This story collection is a classic that I plan to read at least one more time. The translation keeps the text flowing with a style that's simultaneously ancient and contemporary. Also, every tale contains realistic and fantastic elements, and leaves the reader with a handful of ideas to consider afterward. I'd recommend this book to anyone without hesitation.</span>
