<div id="review_415120356" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/415120356" />
    <a title="Florafox" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7631644-florafox"><img alt="Florafox" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1349570290p2/7631644.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/415120356?book_show_action=true">Sep 15, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Florafox" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Florafox" href="/user/show/7631644-florafox">Florafox</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer415120356" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9595560932547633256">The preface was helpful in giving information that would have.been present in the cultural lexicon of contemporary readers of the work, it was, however, so dry that I thought I would never make it to the actual text. thankfully it turned out to be worth slogging through the academic mire. The stories themselves were beautiful, poignant and had the sense of timelessness that is the mark of great literature.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


